  "title": "Struct FastImmutableArray<T>.Enumerator",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Collections_FastImmutableArray_1_Enumerator'>Struct FastImmutableArray&lt;T&gt;.Enumerator    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Math/src/Collections/FastImmutableArray.cs#L1345'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">An array enumerator.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public struct FastImmutableArray&lt;T&gt;.Enumerator</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Remarks</h2><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">It is important that this enumerator does NOT implement <xref href=\"System.IDisposable\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nWe want the iterator to inline when we do foreach and to not result in\na try/finally frame in the client.</p>\n<h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator.#ctor(`0[])' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator.#ctor(`0[])' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Collections_FastImmutableArray_1_Enumerator__ctor__0___'>Enumerator(T[])    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Math/src/Collections/FastImmutableArray.cs#L1365'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray%601.Enumerator\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> struct.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>internal Enumerator(T[] array)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>array</code> T[]  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The array to enumerate.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator._array' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator._array' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Collections_FastImmutableArray_1_Enumerator__array'>_array    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Math/src/Collections/FastImmutableArray.cs#L1350'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The array being enumerated.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private readonly T[] _array</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> T[]  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator._index' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator._index' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Collections_FastImmutableArray_1_Enumerator__index'>_index    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Math/src/Collections/FastImmutableArray.cs#L1359'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The currently enumerated position.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private int _index</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int32'>int</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Properties</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator.Current' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator.Current' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Collections_FastImmutableArray_1_Enumerator_Current'>Current    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Math/src/Collections/FastImmutableArray.cs#L1374'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the currently enumerated value.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public T Current { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> T  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator.MoveNext' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray`1.Enumerator.MoveNext' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Collections_FastImmutableArray_1_Enumerator_MoveNext'>MoveNext()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Math/src/Collections/FastImmutableArray.cs#L1384'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Advances to the next value to be enumerated.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public bool MoveNext()</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Collections.FastImmutableArray-1.Enumerator.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\"><code>true</code> if another item exists in the array; <code>false</code> otherwise.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
